high_descs: Turn right, move forward, then turn right to go around the kitchen island, then turn left to face the counter adjacent to the stove.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Turn right, move forward and turn left at the stove, then look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the egg inside, and cook it, then take it out.
Turn right, go to the counter ahead, then turn right again and go to the wall, then turn left to face the trash bin.
Put the egg in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the trash.

high_descs: Turn right and take three steps then turn right and walk until you are even with the counter just to the left of the stove to your left and then turn left and walk to it when you are even with it.
Pick up the egg that's to the left of the tomato near the wall.
Turn right and walk to the right side of the stove then turn left to face it when you get there.
Cook the egg in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left to face the garbage on the floor.
Put the egg in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved egg in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up an egg.on the counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Cook the egg in the microwave.
Turn and go to the trash can by the refrigerator.
Put the egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Move a microwaved egg to the trashcan.
